  "texts": [
    "However, the electronic health records datasets are still rare, and the EHRs [15] and MD-HER [76] are unavailable.3) Healthcare dialogue: Healthcare dialogue data records the interactions in the healthcare setting between doctors and patients or among the doctors.",
    "These conversations are invaluable for refining communication skills and improving information retrieval processes for LFMs.",
    "There are many publicly available healthcare dialogue datasets [64], [68], [69], [71], [72], [84], [86], [90], [103], [104], [284]- [286], [286], [288], [290]- [293] and some technologies can also transform other healthcare text data or classification labels into dialogue [294].",
    "BianqueCorpus [69], built upon several existing datasets including MedDialog [292], IMCS-21 [283], CHIP-MDCFNPC [295], MedDG [287], cMedQA2 [289], and CMD, results in a substantial Chinese medical dialogue dataset containing 2.4M instances.",
    "For English medical dialogue, Medical Meadow [71] also fused 11 self-created datasets and 7 external datasets, thus a large dataset with 160K instances."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
